name: Hotways Chicken Bali
address: Jl. Cokroaminoto, Ubung Kaja, Kec. Denpasar Utara, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80115, Indonesia
review 1: A must try for spicy fried chicken lovers coz they have different tastes. Panties pizza is also available, the soft and cheesy pizza. Clean, friendly staff, indoor & outdoor seating, crowded and limited parking during meals time.
review 2: Their Nashville chicken are so good! Great spiciness and crispy. If only they open it near seminyak area I will sure eat more often. They not only sells chicken but also a joint food chain with panties pizza. Overall the taste was good, affordable price and you know what, it can make you to crave more.
review 3: The chicken was really great, i just didn't expect the spinach and the scrambled egg is this small. Overall the food is great and the place is clean enough. Will come again.
review 4:
Spicy food lovers rejoice! Not only is Hotway's a good representation of "Nashville Hot Chicken", but their spice levels can and will defeat even the toughest tongues. I HIGHLY recommend trying a calibration piece at level 3, called "fast" before you go for the level 4. And only those who can handle the MOST intense spice should go for level 5.

This is coming from someone who always orders the hottest thing on the menu and usually doesn't struggle with the spice level, even here in Asia. But this level 5 is a serious challenge. So don't go there unless you really want the ordeal.

But assuming you get the right spice level for you, the flavors themselves are delicious. Well worth a trip from wherever you are staying in South Bali.
review 5: have ordered from them twice. chicken is always good, but they've forgot to pack the rice which i should be getting in my order twice now. hopefully something is done about this because come on, people pay to get food, and not getting the food they paid for is not cool.

name: Panties Pizza

review 1: Soft pizza full of mozzarella, yumm.. Ayam geprek was tasty and spicy, available crambled egg and crispy spinach at an additional price. Signature menu is Nashville Hotways chicken wz spicy level 1-5. Affordable prices, fast service and friendly staff. In busy hours will be so crowded and limited parking.
review 2:
The price is affordable

name: Depot Wira
address: Gg. Ratna No.2A, Dusun Mertagangga, Ubung Kaja, Kec. Denpasar Utara, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80116, Indonesia
review 1:
By far, this is best Chinese food restaurant in Bali!

Sapo Tahu (IDR 32k)
Silky Japanese tofu coated with eggs then fried and mixed with spicy-sweet sauce and chopped chicken. I liked this dish..

Ayam saus mentega (butter chicken) - IDR 29k
The sauce has a combination flavour of sweet soy sauce and white pepper.

The place is right across the Ubung bus station which is easy to find and it‚Äôs clean. The price is pretty cheap.

This is my favorite place from when I was a kid until now.
Best Chinese food, the taste a bit different at now, but still the best for me.
review 3: One of the "old" depot or restaurant in Bali. Clean, fast and suitable price. Also the chairs and tables, make me feel in 1990....
